Notes: This column captures the record's timestamp, aligning best with the 'hasRecordDateTime' property for temporal data.
Patient identifiers are best represented through 'hasSubjectPseudoIdentifier' to link patients to conditions.
Diagnosis codes are linked via 'hasCode' property, representing a coded concept.
Creation date is best represented with 'hasDateTime' property for timestamp data.
Organizational code links to the data provider institute via 'hasDataProviderInstitute', representing organizational data.
The organization name can be linked through the same property as org_code, providing organizational context.
